name: Vine Snake
Lore: 'Constricts hapless victims. Prey usually struggles at first, then weakens as strength diminishes. Difficult to spot. Common hazard on less-developed worlds.',
Text: 'Habitat: planet sites (except Hoth). Parasite: Non-droid Character. Each move phase, draw destiny; each time destiny > ability, add 1 to X (X starts at 0). Host is power -X (eaten if power = 0).',
